From 2222222222222222222222222222222222222222 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Wine Developer <developer@winehq.org>
Date: Wed, 27 May 2026 00:02:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 2/6] wineandroid.drv: Add Vulkan WSI skeleton and core data
 structures

Introduce vulkan.c with:
  - Runtime symbol resolution for all API-29+ NDK functions
  - Core structs: wine_vk_surface, wine_vk_buffer, wine_vk_swapchain
  - Wine vulkan driver hook registration (get_vulkan_driver)
  - Stub implementations for every driver entry point
  - android.h additions for the new types and shared declarations

The file compiles and the driver registers successfully; actual rendering
is wired in subsequent patches.

Signed-off-by: Wine Developer <developer@winehq.org>
---
 dlls/wineandroid.drv/android.h | 121 ++++++++++++
 dlls/wineandroid.drv/vulkan.c  | 310 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 dlls/wineandroid.drv/init.c   |  12 +-
 3 files changed, 440 insertions(+), 3 deletions(-)
 create mode 100644 dlls/wineandroid.drv/vulkan.c

